### ML Challenge API Examples
### Use in VS Code with REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@productId = premium-laptop-mx2024

# ==============================================
# Product Detail API
# ==============================================

### Get Product by ID - Success Case
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Product by ID - Alternative Product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/gaming-chair-deluxe
Accept: application/json

### Get Product by ID - Not Found Case
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/nonexistent-product
Accept: application/json

### Get Product by ID - Invalid ID Format
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/123
Accept: application/json

# ==============================================
# Product List API (if implemented)
# ==============================================

### Get All Products - Default
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Get Products with Search Query
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?q=laptop
Accept: application/json

### Get Products with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&limit=12
Accept: application/json

### Get Products with Search and Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?q=gaming&page=1&limit=3
Accept: application/json

### Get Products with Invalid Parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=0&limit=101
Accept: application/json

